<Dynamic Caste System>
{
	Number(7048),
	Description("With the introduction of a new, more flexible caste system, individuals began to strive harder in the hopes of being able to advance their social careers. While one's caste remains largely fixed, the existence of the possibility of advancement becomes an attractive incentive for individuals to become more productive, resulting in heightened overall progress for the classism society on the whole."),
	<Prerequisite>
	[
		Tech(1133),
		Society("Classism")
	],
	Type("Fixed"),
	<Effect>
	{
		Efficiency(2),
		Growth(3),
		Genius(2),
		Diplomacy(2),
		Production(2),
		Military(-3)
	},
	Cost(10000000)
},

<Personality Augmenter>
{
	Number(7049),
	Description("Eventually, it was realised that the essence of a personalist society was its members being able to bring in alot more ideas than the other societies. This eventually led to the development of machines that altered personalities randomly to increase the probability of it discovering a new idea. While this idea was hugely successful upon implementation, the individuals in the society began to see the experiments as undermining basic rights, and started to reject the change."),
	<Prerequisite>
	[
		Tech(1132),
		Society("Personalism")
	],
	Type("Fixed"),
	<Effect>
	{
		Genius(4),
		Efficiency(2),
		Commerce(3),
		Research(3),
		Spy(+2),
		Production(1),
		Growth(-4),
		Diplomacy(-5)
	},
	Cost(10000000)
},

<Unquestionable Authority>
{
	Number(7050),
	Description("The advent of unification was a natural catalyst in the development of autocracies. With the individual minions unable to resist the will of their leaders, it became possible to create warriors with no fear of dying, workers which never grew exhausted and perfect coordination between all these entities. However, this also stymied the mental development of the society, as the individual members become so accustomed to being told what to do, they lose their ability to process new ideas on their own."),
	<Prerequisite>
	[
		Tech(1134),
		Society("Totalism")
	],
	Type("Fixed"),
	<Effect>
	{
		Production(4),
		Efficiency(4),
		Military(4),
