	Description("In their spaceships, wandering from one planet to another, the Buckaneers cannot help but wonder about their race's future. Without a form of government, it was hard to come to a decision. You finally decide that your cooperation with other races has brought along much prosperity, and must ensure that diplomacy with other races is treated even more delicately than before. With that in mind, your people engage in serious diplomatic negaotiations with the next world they reach."),
},

